      "doc": "Sweep the strategy's full balance of `token` to `to`. Used by the\\nrewards module to extract claimed BLND emissions before swapping\\nthem to USDC and redepositing into the vault.\\n\\nRefuses to sweep `asset` (USDC principal) \\xe2\\x80\\x94 that path is reserved\\nfor `withdraw` / `emergency_withdraw`. Callable by `vault`, `admin`,\\nor the configured `rewards_module`. Returns the swept amount; if\\nthe strategy holds zero of `token`, returns 0 without erroring.",
